{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The world around Hungry Joe's Pizza's may have changed, but nothing is going to get in the way of delivering his loyal customers their pies.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the latest employee, your job is to make and deliver the same classic pizzas Joe's has been serving to customers for decades. <i>Just don't ask what happened to the last delivery driver.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/pizza-making.gif?t=1738708881\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by old flash games and the retro era of 3D,\u00a0<strong>Pizza Blitz</strong> is a split between a chill cooking simulator where you make pizzas and <i>vibe</i>, and a hectic score-attack driving game where you must deliver your pizzas in a city under fire.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/drifting.gif?t=1738708881\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Originally a jam game made for <i>Brackey's Game Jam 2024.2</i>, it has now been expanded upon and streamlined to be a more <strong>complete</strong> experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete your 5 day work week, each with a pizza making and delivery section</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine ingredients to craft 11 different  pizza recipes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intense, fast paced delivery gameplay with <i>sleek</i> driving controls and dopamine inducing drifting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Score high points to buy various useful and, really not so useful items for the pizzeria</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">18 unique achievements</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Common